public interface MaterialRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Material,Long>
Repository interface for Material entity operations. Handles database interactions for storing and retrieving study materials.

      List<Material> findByStatus(String status)

      Parameters:
      status - The status to filter by.
      Returns:
      List of materials.

    • findByStatusAndType

      List<Material> findByStatusAndType(String status, String type)
      Finds materials by status and type (e.g., "APPROVED" and "NOTE"). Useful for filtering content on the frontend.
      Parameters:
      status - The approval status.
      type - The type of material (NOTE, PYQ, PROJECT).
      Returns:
      List of matching materials.

    • searchMaterials

      @Query("SELECT m FROM Material m WHERE m.status = 'APPROVED' AND (:subject IS NULL OR m.subject = :subject) AND (:semester IS NULL OR m.semester = :semester) AND (:type IS NULL OR m.type = :type) AND (:query IS NULL OR LOWER(m.title) LIKE LOWER(CONCAT('%', :query, '%')) OR LOWER(m.description) LIKE LOWER(CONCAT('%', :query, '%')))") List<Material> searchMaterials(@Param("subject") String subject, @Param("semester") String semester, @Param("type") String type, @Param("query") String query)
